casebody.data:
No. 11-5506 (11A123). Robert W. Jackson, III, Petitioner v. Delaware. 564 U.S. 1057, 132 S. Ct. 54,

180 L. Ed. 2d 922,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 5081. July 28, 2011.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death, presented to Justice Alito, and by him referred to the Court, denied. Petition for writ of certio-rari to the Supreme Court of Delaware denied.

Same case below, 21 A.3d 27.
